Due to the name mismatch between https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/blob/2efd22454a62e7387c51eb0cd973e5ff7a3fb09f/x-pack/plugin/sql/src/main/java/org/elasticsearch/xpack/sql/expression/function/scalar/math/Sign.java#L37-L40
and
https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/blob/08da5bb5eadd0efd79ba5fad325da29219b89623/x-pack/plugin/sql/src/main/java/org/elasticsearch/xpack/sql/expression/function/scalar/whitelist/InternalSqlScriptUtils.java#L260-L262

The `SIGN`/`SIGNUM` function fail when used in `GROUP BY` or `ORDER BY`. 

To reproduce:

```
SELECT SIGNUM(salary - 50000) sig FROM test_emp GROUP BY sig 
```

